{"tid":340963,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"HKexpress咁樣算唔算違反商品說明條例？","createTime":"2017-07-30T11:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T04:54:44.000Z","uid":131622,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d738a27d69e3581195852f4d244ae113cd1dea3","tid":340963,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">HKexpress官網首頁寫住「香港<span style=\"color: red;\">最準時</span>航空公司」</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/192309_e57b5395434021f44dbe79bc09db10ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F192309_e57b5395434021f44dbe79bc09db10ad.png&h=27312622&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/192318_8a73f7c151ddbd6e07beab05be56a620.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F192318_8a73f7c151ddbd6e07beab05be56a620.png&h=b59b14dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Click入去睇下佢點解咁講</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n「在HK Express，我們高度重視航班的準時率。這不僅有助我們保持健康的營運，亦讓旅客享受良好及可靠的飛行體驗。根據著名獨立飛行資訊網站 <a href=\"http://Flightstats.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFlightstats.com&d=9wUuuD4EdXwN53T3OcOytROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=820ed152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Flightstats.com</a> 網站<a href=\"http://www.flightstats.com/go/FlightRating/flightRatingByCarrier.do?airlineCode=UO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.flightstats.com%2Fgo%2FFlightRating%2FflightRatingByCarrier.do%3FairlineCode%3DUO&d=9wUuuD4EdXwN53T3OcOytROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=b96f085a\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.flightstats.com/go/FlightRating/flightRatingByCarrier.do?airlineCode=UO</a>統計， 我們獲評為香港最準時航空公司，有關數據是計算航班在預定時間十五分鐘內從香港起飛的比率。請繼續留意此頁以得知更多有關資訊！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又click入去 「<a href=\"http://Flightstats.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FFlightstats.com&d=9wUuuD4EdXwN53T3OcOytROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=820ed152\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Flightstats.com</a>」 網站睇下咩統計咩數據</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/30/192638_5d28f8326f39c253eefd9bfedcda9ab3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F30%2F192638_5d28f8326f39c253eefd9bfedcda9ab3.png&h=5028d516&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Page Not Found</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60dabaf3b0d88aada7d21ec05fa2a564d5f6a9f","tid":340963,"uid":64953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"最準時=/=一定準時<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"9b0627c644e4a46c5f0f6ecb6903bf1ee75b3fef","tid":340963,"uid":77717,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:34:17.000Z","msg":"支持你告"},{"pid":"866ef4620817a30b7c122195f2287606eee65d7c","tid":340963,"uid":101550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T11:37:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最準時=/=一定準時<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n証明唔到自己係最就等於失實<br />\n以前公司training都有講<br />\n如果冇數據支持而用個最字就拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d417038d81498a7d84daba985a9defb87d4195","tid":340963,"uid":131622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"<block